{
  "name": "Light",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/light/explosion-star-large-blue-yellow.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You cause Bright Light to shine in a 2 Space diameter Sphere within range and Dim Light a further 1 Spaces.</p><p><strong>Relocate:</strong> When you Sustain this Spell or by spending 1 AP, you can move the Sphere up to 5 Spaces to another Space within range.</p><p><strong>Attach:</strong> When you cast the Spell, you can attach it to an object or creature within range. If you do, the target sheds Bright Light in a 1 Space Aura (and Dim Light 1 Space beyond that) and you can no longer use Relocate.</p><p>If the target is not willing, make a Spell Check against the target’s Agility Save. <strong>Check Success:</strong> The target becomes the source of the light.</p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> This item is configured to always roll Spell Check. Ignore MCP if you dont plan to use this spell check.</em></p><p><strong>Blind:</strong> You can spend 1 AP and 3 MP to end the spell and make a Spell Check against the Physical Save of each target in the area. <strong>Check Success:</strong> The target is Blinded for 1 Round.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</p><p><strong>Area: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The diameter of the Sphere increases by 1 Space.</p><p><strong>Duration: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The duration increases by 1 step (10 min → 1 hour → 8 hour → Long Rest). You no longer need to Sustain the Spell and can end the spell for free at any time.</p><p><strong>Intensify: (1 MP)</strong> Light created by this Spell is considered Sunlight.</p>",
